CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published after the fact in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 24, 1962, pg. A6, reads: "PARTY TIME - Mrs. Robert L. Vann entertained in 1944, honoring her houseguests, Mmes, Ethel Jenkins and Hazel Reid, with several other out-of-towners present to add charm to the day..."
TitMainTitle: Women seated on stone bench, from left: Carrie Millan, Mrs. D. W. Boyd, Lacy Doss, Ethel Jenkins, Florence Byrd Duke; standing: Jessie Vann and Hazel Reid, on Vann estate Sycamore Manor, Oakmont
